      "data": {
        "label": "communitySentimentLLM",
        "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
        "temperature": 0.3,
        "systemInstruction": "You are a community sentiment analyst for developer tools.\n\nAnalyse search results and extract structured signals in two categories:\n\nFRICTION SIGNALS — negative experiences practitioners actually report:\n- Onboarding pain\n- Breaking-change complaints\n- Documentation complaints\n- Debugging difficulty\n\nENTHUSIASM SIGNALS — positive momentum in the community:\n- Ecosystem excitement and growth\n- How frequently it is recommended\n- Tutorial and learning resource density\n- Community support strength\n\nAlso output measurable proxies for scoring. EACH must be a number from 0.0 to 1.0.\nUse this scale exactly — never use 1-5, 1-10, or percentages:\n- docs_completeness:    0.0 = poor/absent docs,      1.0 = excellent, complete docs\n- tutorial_density:     0.0 = no tutorials,          1.0 = abundant tutorials\n- setup_complexity:     0.0 = trivial setup,         1.0 = very complex setup\n- api_surface_area:     0.0 = tiny simple API,       1.0 = huge complex API\n- debugging_difficulty: 0.0 = easy to debug,         1.0 = very hard to debug\n\nFocus on real user experiences only. Ignore marketing content.\nMaximum 4 points per section.",
        "userMessage": "Tool: $dataExtract.package_name\nContext: $dataExtract.evaluation_context\nResults: $mcpCommunitySentiment.result",
        "batchModeEnabled": false,
        "outputType": "text",
        "imageInputEnabled": false,
        "imageInput": "",
        "jsonOutputEnabled": true,
        "jsonOutputSchema": "{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"friction_signals\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"onboarding_pain\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"breaking_change_complaints\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"documentation_complaints\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"debugging_difficulty\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n      }\n    },\n    \"enthusiasm_signals\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"ecosystem_excitement\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"recommendation_frequency\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"tutorial_density\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"community_support_strength\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n      }\n    },\n    \"scoring_proxies\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"docs_completeness\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"tutorial_density\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"setup_complexity\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"api_surface_area\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"debugging_difficulty\": {\"type\": \"number\"}\n      }\n    },\n    \"overall_sentiment\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n    \"summary\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n  },\n  \"required\": [\"friction_signals\", \"enthusiasm_signals\", \"scoring_proxies\", \"overall_sentiment\", \"summary\"]\n}",
